node.text:
#𝗙𝗔𝗜𝗟𝗨𝗥𝗘 can be painful but it 𝗗𝗢𝗘𝗦 𝗡𝗢𝗧 𝗗𝗘𝗙𝗜𝗡𝗘 𝗬𝗢𝗨. Failure is just a life experience to be 𝘧𝘢𝘤𝘦𝘥, 𝘥𝘦𝘢𝘭𝘵 𝘸𝘪𝘵𝘩 and 𝘭𝘦𝘢𝘳𝘯𝘦𝘥 𝘧𝘳𝘰𝘮.
⁣
Have you ever felt like a failure? You aren't one until you start to blame others and give up.

You can always learn from your failures until you start to 𝗱𝗲𝗻𝘆 them. ⁣
⁣⁣
I love failing - because I would never have gotten to where I am today if I made excuses and didn’t learn from them.

#embraceyourfailures #failureispartofsuccess #failureisnotfinal #failureissuccess #failureislearning #failure #fail

#DeeboMode #DeeboGear
